{
  "stem": "23278.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As then she came to Dijon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know for sure what her parents were doing, but they were rich.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She had little button nose, curly hair, green eyes, teeth like pearls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was the most prettiest girl I had seen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, I am not a lesbian or anything, but I was sensitive to her beauty.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was fun.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were good friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she invited me to her house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And her house was the first house I saw with wall-to-wall carpeting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't have that at home-- and beautiful things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one day, she went to the library of her father where she had very nice bound book.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she told me-- she gave me the book of-- a book by [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was in German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she said, I give you that to remember me by.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because I like that book.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] .",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a novel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, you know, in France, you know, had this system.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it's very intelligent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In school, we wore smocks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were ecru colored, you know, beige.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had our name embroidered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But everybody was the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So whether you were rich or poor, when you were in school, you were all dressed the same.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you left it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have any locker, because there was no theft, nothing like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We left it on a hook with our class section.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Beatrice told me, you know, tomorrow, I'm going to be here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you'll tell that I'm sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in a week, you just take my smock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you can use it for yourself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You just take off the name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I have an aunt in Venezuela, and we are going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we kissed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We cried, and OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
